### 1. Quá trình hình thành và phát triển
Viện Kế toán – Kiểm toán được thành lập theo **Quyết định số 178/QĐ-ĐHTHN-TCNS** của Hiệu trưởng. Tiền thân là Khoa Kế toán – Kiểm toán được thành lập ngay từ khi thành lập Trường. Là một trong những đơn vị chủ lực, phát triển không ngừng về quy mô và chất lượng.', '[-0.085041195,0.050773356,0.016888794,-0.026234312,-0.0369044,0.040332217,0.054798476,-0.05920474,0.00896979,0.0847647,0.056580126,-0.033565123,-0.009443639,0.03875755,0.045792136,-0.041850366,-0.030543951,0.058025233,-0.07074711,0.0362102,0.08336063,-0.07016142,0.049218114,-0.016397672,-0.03885725,-0.03578539,0.046967074,0.07241572,-0.075925216,-0.12608357,-0.03286544,0.027483547,-0.009721437,-0.0335828,0.047958147,-0.057803508,-0.03243695,0.05342348,0.038461376,0.048866525,-0.02068675,-0.054413058,0.016673297,-0.075682856,0.04096493,-0.01767356,-0.07096601,-0.05533107,0.0673542,0.011712943,-0.062479634,-0.017565884,0.06726203,0.06265621,0.026067812,0.048262294,0.016754212,0.030577341,0.07525474,0.06355724,0.016445847,0.06205379,-0.13349034,0.13525718,0.088055246,0.050548065,-0.017310997,0.013354111,-0.033972252,-0.005622889,0.016789835,0.062352996,0.034775328,0.038220767,-0.05396791,0.06460071,0.055082936,0.068377055,-0.082552895,-0.035063036,-0.036302112,-0.031840373,-0.0063513834,-0.018738167,-0.04474199,-0.005295886,0.022752402,-0.020587081,-0.010844632,-0.0040414217,-0.0041190544,-0.035864517,0.017940028,-0.011651437,-0.019697998,-0.06287223,0.026934616,0.0426005,-0.028344324,0.09535005,-0.00787326,0.030876761,-0.039594,-0.089534804,-0.034646552,-0.0020280504,0.05454411,-0.04245537,0.0635171,-0.04831094,-0.061677907,-0.04613743,0.023601942,-0.016588032,0.037693933,0.027910676,-0.02060986,-0.082606785,-0.037385426,0.05410246,0.044529434,0.020569684,0.009222461,-0.043751482,0.04457391,-0.035734724,0.06465014,0.055231206,0.063473135,-0.021093357,0.04147605,-0.01754409,-0.013793019,-0.056007218,-0.039910782,-0.052981265,-0.036219027,-0.02228803,0.04018801,-0.033466253,-0.020131506,-0.123769626,-0.00129