Viện Quản trị – Kinh doanh được thành lập theo **Quyết định 177/QĐ-ĐHTNH-TCNS ngày 16/12/2020** trên cơ sở Khoa Quản trị – Kinh doanh. Viện đào tạo ngành Quản trị kinh doanh và Kinh doanh thương mại từ năm học 2012-2013. Tính đến tháng 12/2023, đã tuyển 12 khóa, tốt nghiệp 8 khóa.', '[-0.12128837,0.038954437,0.059973452,-0.0087301545,-0.0355069,0.051030558,0.018555073,-0.053432178,0.021003522,0.05316077,0.06869797,-0.014708405,-0.04251003,0.02298831,0.0044314894,-0.0684694,-0.029356366,0.043723736,-0.058060464,0.04389598,0.08658716,-0.065028705,0.04075569,-0.041239917,-0.021248488,-0.02081782,0.042334784,0.08315758,-0.07010842,-0.12551709,-0.031236414,0.017488157,-0.01047371,-0.032937083,0.063013434,-0.050151918,-0.021546546,0.06454812,0.02561526,0.04846591,-0.03092116,-0.04551991,0.022041367,-0.062355366,0.03815357,-0.0067884116,-0.06671776,-0.03974666,0.08332045,0.030987257,-0.0520237,-0.013859402,0.06557755,0.058549326,0.02264655,0.039661035,-0.0024634774,0.045843475,0.07816681,0.06835191,0.023662727,0.058126565,-0.11832905,0.110803716,0.07496702,0.060878336,-0.03057387,0.0085907625,-0.013533571,-0.040855758,0.013598258,0.060199775,0.029322052,0.029637733,-0.048532277,0.051893465,0.024710003,0.073850356,-0.083207525,-0.050158273,-0.038587157,-0.012521338,-0.0044093593,0.009878281,-0.024557326,-0.023347665,0.03271915,-0.0046740016,-0.034014095,-0.024235062,-0.01427674,-0.031709734,0.03271922,-0.031615026,-0.03643529,-0.047753584,0.036608938,0.053031653,-0.040397126,0.07805539,0.0147517435,0.012946871,-0.03413786,-0.062141452,-0.025508597,-0.027314093,0.040776663,-0.021107016,0.045420427,-0.025745502,-0.057063866,-0.05292226,0.022490205,-0.030521048,0.018646656,0.04057902,-0.03720383,-0.09218629,-0.047302388,0.032806087,0.027838616,0.027617833,0.008953119,-0.03474243,0.055984553,-0.039321028,0.045838077,0.060207967,0.060182612,0.007028725,0.054673206,-0.003965307,-0.0020386751,-0.030129269,-0.029322041,-0.044324677,-0.041242257,-0.026436383,0.050646707,-0.024695158