#### 2.4. Các Hội đồng của Viện
- **Hội đồng Khoa học Viện Kế toán – Kiểm toán:** Tập hợp chuyên gia hàng đầu về Kế toán, Kiểm toán, thống kê, phân tích kinh tế; tư vấn khoa học, tham gia đào tạo, trợ giúp nghiên cứu.
- **Quỹ thắp sáng tình yêu kế toán – kiểm toán:** Tạo lập từ tài trợ, đóng góp của giảng viên, phụ huynh; khích lệ sinh viên ưu tú.', '[-0.107569106,0.043343876,0.023442123,-0.013535835,-0.028356388,0.0644849,0.055935465,-0.07218842,0.03420324,0.08313245,0.05122221,-0.022604896,-0.026625402,0.02701323,0.036217235,-0.032082047,-0.060088523,0.07090899,-0.09316231,0.04155355,0.075922385,-0.03635605,0.03432177,-0.019665744,-0.03097498,-0.025474314,0.04136914,0.06345049,-0.062788166,-0.11889479,-0.040105414,0.024919013,-0.008482671,-0.022237338,0.047229484,-0.050358895,-0.016028313,0.06406838,0.029075885,0.03932749,-0.032280847,-0.04597475,-0.008257829,-0.0652213,0.03252633,0.0043429458,-0.075063996,-0.032768346,0.0740158,0.0289132,-0.058412567,-0.002159022,0.054390587,0.06605152,0.02339514,0.056891058,0.021759426,0.027265964,0.07517052,0.0713165,0.019494189,0.07054967,-0.13517417,0.1560712,0.101880446,0.06336112,-0.018645098,0.024651079,-0.03776743,-0.031845886,0.014494141,0.053302113,0.028139073,0.032008454,-0.07717116,0.06544293,0.05460269,0.079133265,-0.12129491,-0.01938841,-0.029357722,-0.031860884,-0.025717929,-0.015963325,-0.031991653,-0.015330308,0.020436026,-0.0370205,-0.038973466,-0.028090082,0.008821887,-0.026347501,0.009279634,-0.051794235,-0.018782666,-0.07515185,0.052312426,0.04872334,-0.041844316,0.067746,-0.0072368965,0.03704798,-0.037435792,-0.07892644,-0.03993842,-0.008313982,0.051034804,-0.026403641,0.040617213,-0.027571881,-0.062906735,-0.03644526,0.03336747,-0.03220936,0.03491393,0.014515546,-0.0101689985,-0.09282593,-0.043933973,0.023439491,0.04637601,0.018590003,-0.012140149,-0.014534482,0.06174922,-0.033576295,0.06781842,0.05862182,0.06699805,-0.03762125,0.054824073,-0.013812373,0.013942076,-0.052281488,-0.021940935,-0.048866127,-0.046015628,-0.034641527,0.05473944,-0.014991689,-0.010959816,-0.12333407,-0.018803397,-0.088621594,0.009902322,0.07940043,-0.08829179,0.021827819,-0.049675334,-0.04633569,-0.02345415,-0.005338982,0.07283173,-0.0030418264