> Thông tin về quá trình hình thành, lãnh đạo viện, chuyên ngành đào tạo, bộ môn trực thuộc và các tổ chức Đảng – Đoàn thể.

Viện Công nghệ Thông tin có tên gọi chính thức từ ngày **16/12/2020** theo Quyết định số 179/QĐ-ĐHTNH-TCNS của Hiệu trưởng (trước đây là Khoa Công nghệ Thông tin). Viện đã phát triển song song với quá trình hình thành và hoàn thiện của Nhà trường.', '[-0.09236871,0.030158857,0.042364493,-0.010422285,-0.030915778,0.06148001,0.027428737,-0.05443538,0.01884125,0.06536453,0.06958125,-0.028003292,-0.018038236,0.015713988,0.022475135,-0.05102114,-0.044467937,0.06423796,-0.05906933,0.042267404,0.08076612,-0.07205144,0.029059976,-0.048075955,-0.040925786,-0.03676298,0.032062713,0.06189269,-0.059195638,-0.12821643,-0.05396216,0.03565749,-0.012450352,-0.03684421,0.05034016,-0.067059435,-0.014111712,0.0913519,0.04607272,0.036231954,-0.03850609,-0.0563444,0.027728813,-0.065526746,0.024386784,-0.0025660659,-0.08152501,-0.057544664,0.071023986,0.024718726,-0.05115748,-0.007734341,0.058500312,0.038050033,0.026046114,0.047701456,0.0017765587,0.05111362,0.08447806,0.045012426,0.03169823,0.058131043,-0.12316724,0.122192785,0.076681934,0.05897763,-0.026964897,0.002666816,-0.022950279,-0.027203508,0.01030885,0.0698081,0.058371976,0.03285136,-0.042935118,0.04151151,0.034471083,0.076260574,-0.080352776,-0.05240823,-0.025187483,-0.012371429,-0.003985387,-0.01235705,-0.032027256,-0.0110758515,0.039361645,-0.01224348,-0.013448924,-0.020251825,-0.013065654,-0.045949478,0.011264027,-0.038550556,-0.04317769,-0.040847167,0.04046171,0.067190774,-0.03924888,0.09315817,0.0027568215,0.034154117,-0.041500814,-0.07193713,-0.051423885,-0.00482119,0.03753093,-0.012777633,0.049888592,-0.011923916,-0.071386,-0.044400368,0.029859407,-0.030740194,0.041755322,0.029620096,-0.028142,-0.09041641,-0.051408824,0.03169369,0.037783377,0.008187347,0.005473532,-0.020220421,0.05859533,-0.035170253,0.0638325,0.055099513,0.04654331,0.014319445,0.063274294,-0.018240672,0.013230182,-0.03907077,-0.029794527,-0.06369567,-0.044437684,-0.03762354,0.044968132,-0.028973807,0.0009987897,-0.106277704,-0.022266058,-0.10790802,0.0