### I. Quá trình hình thành và phát triển
> Từ khi thành lập (2017), viện quản lý đào tạo chuyên ngành Tin Ứng Dụng.

- Thành lập năm 2017 với tên Khoa Công nghệ Thông tin.
- Đội ngũ giảng viên 100% trình độ thạc sĩ trở lên.
- Đào tạo trình độ Đại học chính quy.
- Phát triển vượt bậc cả chất và lượng, trở thành địa chỉ tin cậy cho thí sinh.', '[-0.09184968,0.04706721,0.027561722,0.00074205454,-0.03400416,0.056221694,0.046085905,-0.0607382,0.01033682,0.062765166,0.050116673,-0.059137225,-0.043754723,0.013924219,0.042144254,-0.037424255,-0.023672666,0.053988565,-0.06909851,0.023852805,0.07302228,-0.07509058,0.0662642,-0.023494223,-0.03277727,-0.021335615,0.045718227,0.06733746,-0.048619956,-0.104872584,-0.026927175,0.037779883,-0.009850959,-0.07057551,0.060102005,-0.06557013,-0.04222073,0.05349477,0.03674195,0.03716339,-0.044836316,-0.046916787,0.035577137,-0.05636632,0.041896164,-0.009640849,-0.0806084,-0.043312833,0.05336362,0.026375635,-0.06256917,-0.013717008,0.07235519,0.0399618,0.012860575,0.050815552,0.0030249327,0.06432533,0.08097287,0.06545047,0.018584576,0.065017484,-0.13407466,0.13966572,0.09090562,0.03649534,-0.048857205,0.008732038,-0.021035416,-0.04163824,0.004915551,0.06711146,0.031320617,0.032862138,-0.046871554,0.047311924,0.041350164,0.07121475,-0.07746702,-0.022955738,-0.037841424,-0.031103004,-0.016646426,0.010805631,-0.0047674445,-0.009302634,0.04288431,-0.004993147,-0.01754433,-0.027242292,-0.012502259,-0.040496364,0.030973379,-0.031888098,-0.022559453,-0.049125936,0.031090802,0.04952847,-0.028482582,0.10112302,-0.0018067632,0.050680142,-0.008668823,-0.06388748,-0.024993094,-0.0042458186,0.03949761,-0.01391748,0.034298047,-0.015132768,-0.085184045,-0.03820344,0.034213673,-0.02210402,0.035547215,0.060260814,-0.022982508,-0.060753036,-0.02720478,0.04684132,0.024861993,0.012151343,-0.0068696374,-0.013074861,0.039466824,-0.041141264,0.07574464,0.04455194,0.0688029,0.0030617083,0.042970076,-0.014091478,0.001797143,-0.033360556,-0.03723153,-0.07003038,-0.044882853,-0.044569537,0.051576547,-0.05244611,-0.015507296,-0.11441388,-0.008654157,-0.101252005,0.0062416745,0.044892434,-0.09882731,0.03118673,-0.05157995,-0.06903545,-0.018129494,-0.024864197,0.06360101,0.0023871444,0.0001260186,-0.00037445955,0.003434189,