### 2. Sứ mệnh và tầm nhìn
- **Sứ mệnh:** Phát triển chương trình đào tạo theo chuẩn mực quốc tế, đào tạo nguồn nhân lực chất lượng cao có tư duy toàn cầu, năng lực hội nhập, thích ứng linh hoạt.
- **Tầm nhìn:** Trở thành đơn vị đào tạo và hợp tác quốc tế uy tín trong lĩnh vực tài chính, ngân hàng, kinh doanh và quản trị; nâng cao vị thế và thương hiệu FBU.', '[-0.086565696,0.030017713,0.0118657565,-0.008260784,-0.04187038,0.05147219,0.05207834,-0.055517145,0.012832327,0.06881785,0.05491078,-0.033495765,-0.022310648,0.018724943,0.02071646,-0.03443174,-0.056144252,0.076590315,-0.08011624,0.047401648,0.08280927,-0.046899844,0.037604798,-0.02158148,-0.04504851,-0.040239576,0.031346135,0.06213318,-0.056480426,-0.11760934,-0.029782474,0.03601957,-0.025792385,-0.042604815,0.05674317,-0.059660427,-0.031770516,0.065263994,0.035594057,0.041143697,-0.036927618,-0.017460562,0.03612718,-0.05536809,0.03057284,0.009565001,-0.06921515,-0.052997172,0.06071956,0.025326647,-0.06180601,0.0023840133,0.02669841,0.05297743,0.029572226,0.048430208,0.018077776,0.023903942,0.09376353,0.066741355,0.020441221,0.07163938,-0.15528125,0.13650185,0.08671034,0.07031848,-0.01704378,0.018300986,-0.010966569,-0.016263217,0.01651226,0.060173303,0.003947792,0.025810856,-0.06411785,0.061731927,0.042920228,0.07290942,-0.087824635,-0.02849201,-0.034307737,-0.01520584,-0.033217233,-0.0037183238,-0.038361557,-0.004713955,0.020502307,-0.0348224,-0.026591828,-0.023350155,-0.012976394,-0.030147348,0.012982095,-0.03690689,-0.024501465,-0.05403127,0.033421066,0.054885197,-0.02806119,0.06620323,0.004545779,0.025978738,-0.022097522,-0.08804861,-0.042466246,-0.016035613,0.03212034,-0.031285133,0.053455733,-0.020228786,-0.06227505,-0.0415548,0.04048137,-0.018840913,0.030608352,0.03288015,0.004056263,-0.07685519,-0.040536877,0.019677334,0.044522434,0.0051897136,0.010248384,-0.02904933,0.058070466,-0.022021472,0.05814144,0.051590964,0.058801223,-0.018228242,0.050902363,0.006078274,0.017413622,-0.059626583,-0.04733707,-0.058923274,-0.03581041,-0.037418727,0.041873556,-0.04309948,-0.0050036972,-0.120830975,-0.026193786,-0.09539917,0.017596584,0.048910577,-0.08476813,0.012670466,-0.055270456,-0.038065743,-0.00219