#### 3.2. Hợp tác quốc tế
- Là đầu mối tham mưu, tổ chức hoạt động hợp tác quốc tế về đào tạo, nghiên cứu, trao đổi học thuật.
- Thiết lập, duy trì, phát triển quan hệ với các đối tác quốc tế.
- Ký kết, triển khai thỏa thuận hợp tác; quản lý, giám sát chương trình, dự án.
- Tổ chức trao đổi sinh viên, giảng viên, hội thảo quốc tế.', '[-0.085228525,0.047333058,0.013961547,-0.008806607,-0.05027352,0.08108585,0.043361437,-0.065400794,0.012665694,0.06961599,0.039259914,-0.060726907,-0.029548781,0.0022496448,0.040069014,-0.025691945,-0.060265355,0.100269206,-0.08836294,0.013858128,0.08116137,-0.02379767,0.050566435,-0.030733222,-0.038248006,-0.05093887,0.027584141,0.061213385,-0.040589232,-0.1097381,-0.06484121,0.05354193,-0.006535178,-0.041332696,0.045688704,-0.05888741,-0.038449563,0.03906372,0.020247443,0.049990423,-0.033441123,-0.02719365,0.002663164,-0.03830476,0.02775701,0.016810749,-0.080287695,-0.043028686,0.067334555,0.032055408,-0.058177765,0.006800624,0.055009436,0.063863896,0.022521246,0.05639404,0.03537337,0.036878843,0.08620421,0.067195885,0.015763298,0.075241394,-0.11809903,0.15125787,0.09727435,0.063174754,-0.021460157,0.008612497,-0.059560053,-0.009135656,0.01740308,0.06400411,-0.010650989,0.046577334,-0.04629547,0.04219236,0.04582229,0.062969826,-0.09246895,-0.00047528264,-0.024117876,-0.02056056,-0.009140293,-0.017438415,-0.030500012,-0.0029652861,0.036327116,-0.02655882,-0.020877957,-0.03675557,-0.0059857015,-0.049139842,0.021885391,-0.064013936,-0.022406435,-0.073704496,0.048973225,0.03924689,-0.013201113,0.07704413,-0.0045759645,0.035809338,-0.030252635,-0.08017223,-0.014833814,-0.0039372495,0.04870738,-0.021747276,0.07060641,-0.0051676333,-0.09046087,-0.043543562,0.048307475,-0.03666923,0.029189307,0.04381184,-0.025332963,-0.0664621,-0.005237381,0.03833849,0.036539797,-0.009679713,-0.000752254,-0.0005086292,0.05369317,-0.04298434,0.06933045,0.058480337,0.055091254,-0.019013107,0.05338817,-0.017108798,-0.0009687073,-0.04075221,-0.037991762,-0.044461727,-0.043997724,-0.038801707,0.040418334,-0.029688852,0.00728237,-0.109224916,-0.0042066947,-0.084112756,0.018242644,0.06994515,-0.07536013,0.025328502,-0.034712087,-0.051519293,-0.019164633,-0.030247971,0.06586483,-0.0017594316,-0.0017373033,0.021625888,-0.01682028,0.075