### Câu hỏi 2: Chứng chỉ quốc phòng trong trường hợp không tìm thấy thì còn cách nào khác ngoài học lại không?
**Trả lời:**  
Bạn đừng quá lo lắng! Việc mất chứng chỉ GDQP-AN hoàn toàn có thể xin cấp lại, miễn là bạn đã hoàn thành khóa học do trường tổ chức. Cụ thể:

- **Trường hợp học chứng chỉ qua đợt trường tổ chức:** Bạn đến **Phòng Công tác sinh viên và Phục vụ cộng đồng (CTSV&PVCD)** hoặc **Phòng Khảo thí** để làm đơn xin cấp lại. Nhà trường có lưu hồ sơ và quyết định công nhận chứng chỉ, do đó bạn vẫn được công nhận hoàn thành môn học mà không cần học lại.', '[-0.105611354,0.038864557,-0.004602184,-0.028540397,-0.035201203,0.0683141,0.05547451,-0.066152126,0.004022316,0.085244104,0.061908677,-0.012807797,-0.0068366006,0.015823893,0.0069623506,-0.026668778,-0.06901331,0.06986185,-0.1070936,0.039262075,0.060399644,-0.03977643,0.023734791,-0.020361379,-0.04249033,-0.047172796,0.023590056,0.046929885,-0.07862374,-0.12342739,-0.058809824,0.014806276,-0.0019591574,-0.055233486,0.039879862,-0.07010745,-0.025787583,0.068105415,0.040011603,0.025539907,-0.040996455,-0.03800046,0.018428348,-0.034397867,-0.015932756,0.034881003,-0.0771195,-0.029370535,0.06427898,0.029808555,-0.07369076,0.019281918,0.08339285,0.048490256,-0.003920788,0.08614752,0.03408511,0.04262745,0.09663799,0.08817463,-0.0071659414,0.06936471,-0.17277962,0.16869731,0.10041031,0.07018552,-0.037948392,0.013265817,-0.00037306017,-0.013747878,0.014872107,0.034062423,-0.015791722,0.023823356,-0.06029304,0.08079956,0.01947622,0.0965689,-0.08541409,-0.026209623,-0.029098794,-0.01539693,-0.019554976,0.020973148,-0.04752747,0.0013135271,0.042679243,-0.0108333025,-0.030284952,-0.014449683,0.008212723,-0.03443508,-0.009475789,-0.057447214,-0.013187066,-0.043974333,0.055647347,0.05752988,-0.05062369,0.07326072,0.01778012,0.035045423,-0.016911017,-0.07877305,-0.052044623,-0.0030570112,0.043787085,-0.038493887,0.043848693,-0.011294594,-0.06940135,-0.02385395,0.071481034,-0.029798904,0.04588822,0.037844777,0.013858406,-0.06846681,-0.047080167,0.006805597,0.041396145,-0.024690067,-0.006825656,-0.009982292,0.060099,-0.026704205,0.053990856,0.05698453,0.047580466,-0.020556644,0.065207586,-0.004112633,0.044246458,-0.025018493,-0.040062763,-0.05520078,-0.053961877,-0.03464947,0.046889