### Điều 3. Thời gian và điều kiện xét học bổng
a) Xét duyệt theo từng học kỳ, sau khi có kết quả học tập và rèn luyện.
b) Sinh viên không vi phạm kỷ luật từ mức khiển trách trở lên.
c) Đối tượng tại khoản 1 và mục a,b khoản 2 Điều 2: kết quả học tập ≥ 5.5 (thang 10, lần thi cao nhất), rèn luyện loại Khá trở lên. Xét trong 04 năm học (08 kỳ).
d) Đối tượng tại mục c khoản 2 Điều 2: trong năm thứ nhất, kết quả học tập HK I và II ≥ 7.0 (lần 1, thang 10), rèn luyện Tốt trở lên. Xét trong năm thứ nhất (tối đa 2 kỳ).
e) Sinh viên bị kỷ luật ngừng học, buộc thôi học, bảo lưu không được xét.', '[-0.11564844,0.028405651,0.016846769,-0.019707011,-0.038251508,0.043532476,0.030519966,-0.058453828,0.025079483,0.05622808,0.072241776,-0.031103102,-0.008488656,0.019246425,0.038167153,-0.028350938,-0.054851677,0.09993998,-0.09006489,0.04462228,0.07743515,-0.047873233,0.020328471,-0.050098084,-0.022584485,-0.041484725,0.016311167,0.04754077,-0.05079089,-0.117731,-0.033350673,0.04769173,-0.0053082807,-0.05213068,0.06238956,-0.07517261,-0.014016731,0.06093266,0.039969016,0.04467461,-0.029001206,-0.039500535,0.0041904096,-0.06582773,-9.087301e-05,0.018426284,-0.072906256,-0.0497619,0.070603654,0.021970447,-0.06771546,-0.011118602,0.064701535,0.04203346,0.021650845,0.03805545,0.041787315,0.027418714,0.08088592,0.0737132,0.003455553,0.065470986,-0.1316573,0.14783603,0.111454114,0.0559913,-0.03332873,0.017519765,-0.031604465,0.0046762642,0.014670786,0.025188997,0.009276551,0.04052746,-0.057407465,0.076580085,0.025170745,0.08773877,-0.096501246,-0.023635566,-0.05598285,-0.043298814,-0.029867407,-0.0027413059,-0.008307903,-0.025925472,0.0015694085,-0.025548896,-0.038429026,-0.025150849,-0.014196042,-0.022070227,0.016184038,-0.06398935,0.0014851325,-0.07080756,0.06622644,0.052738216,-0.04343793,0.08521592,0.02012208,0.031982098,-0.04081359,-0.081203155,-0.03645532,-0.012814601,0.031878218,-0.03255334,0.044913087,-0.028796677,-0.078641884,-0.03967004,0.056314666,-0.03163362,0.03983215,0.015416466,-0.017011505,-0.05855901,-0.03255295,0.0041792034,0.046108298,-0.024472017,0.01789629,-0.026240045,0.038030405,-0.02770064,0.056727916,0.06968487,0.047312133,-0.014508611,0.06978033,-0.020126166,0.014819449,-0.030389521,-0.051246844,-0.07593099,-0.039069206,-0.04523833,0.050185893,-0.040263228,0.0014310293,-0.115104035,-0.010202521,-0.069923386,0.029894542,0.09734859,-0.08749246,0.02106552,-0.035176586,-0.07799508,-0.016475659,-0.020511566,0.040306583,0.0043060305,-0.022620577,0.031028328,-0.0015208662,0.110