### II. Đối với sinh viên chưa được phê duyệt (xét bổ sung kỳ I+II/2025-2026)
| Đối tượng | Mức chi trả | Hồ sơ |
|-----------|-------------|-------|
| 1. Người có công với cách mạng (theo Pháp lệnh) | 100% | Đơn (PL IV), giấy xác nhận của cơ quan quản lý người có công, giấy xác nhận cư trú. |
| 2. Sinh viên khuyết tật | 100% | Đơn (PL IV), giấy xác nhận khuyết tật, QĐ trợ cấp xã hội, giấy xác nhận cư trú. |
| 3. Người 16-22 tuổi đang học đại học (văn bằng thứ nhất) thuộc đối tượng bảo trợ xã hội | 100% | Đơn (PL IV), QĐ trợ cấp xã hội, giấy xác nhận cư trú. |
| 4. Sinh viên dân tộc thiểu số có cha/mẹ/ông bà thuộc hộ nghèo/cận nghèo | 100% | Đơn (PL IV), giấy xác nhận hộ nghèo/cận nghèo, giấy khai sinh (photo công chứng), giấy xác nhận cư trú. |
| 5. Sinh viên dân tộc thiểu số rất ít người (Cống, Mảng, Pu Péo, Si La, Cơ Lao, Bố Y, La Ha, Ngái, Chứt, Ơ Đu, Brâu, Rơ Măm, Lô Lô, Lự, Pà Thẻn, La Hủ) ở vùng khó khăn | 100% | Đơn (PL IV), giấy xác nhận dân tộc thiểu số rất ít người và hộ khẩu khu vực I, giấy xác nhận cư trú, giấy khai sinh. |
| 6. Sinh viên dân tộc thiểu số (không rất ít) có nơi thường trú tại thôn/bản đặc biệt khó khăn, xã khu vực III, xã đặc biệt khó khăn | 70% | Đơn (PL IV), giấy xác nhận dân tộc thiểu số, hộ khẩu khu vực II, giấy xác nhận cư trú, giấy khai sinh. |
| 7. Sinh viên là con cán bộ, công chức, viên chức, công nhân bị tai nạn lao động/mắc bệnh nghề nghiệp được hưởng trợ cấp thường xuyên | 50% | Đơn (PL IV), QĐ hưởng trợ cấp hàng tháng của cha/mẹ, giấy xác nhận cư trú, giấy khai sinh. |', '[-0.086518906,0.034987904,-0.0061362423,-0.011082097,-0.021886954,0.031244125,0.024944467,-0.059348963,0.015145909,0.07296912,0.07728226,-0.024074862,0.008545842,0.033801127,-0.0036073371,-0.041813828,-0.06711676,0.045097727,-0.12134818,0.02380846,0.0833097,-0.031789184,0.019826423,-0.055629615,-0.005239395,-0.024857048,0.041320294,0.07591902,-0.07884707,-0.12698679,-0.031904694,0.049010463,-0.024837326,-0.025944425,0.06947846,-0.05936754,-0.029554266,0.079903334,0.022755517,0.040355466,-0.025394877,-0.03520449,0.0084332535,-0.057100654,0.011169253,0.009180163,-0.08297807,-0.065267004,0.08040707,0.01112598,-0.07403862,-0.0042176256,0.06672376,0.042324632,0.0041902936,0.040423427,0.02486548,0.04398444,0.10947671,0.07481581,0.009753378,0.06366192,-0.12116899,0.14836864,0.0793735,0.052545153,-0.037514478,0.020386633,-0.014411729,0.009893865,0.015786977,0.024069164,0.0010677561,0.031038709,-0.07419887,0.061380837,0.04241656,0.06416404,-0.098093525,-0.045386128,-0.032129813,-0.015175734,-8.475726e-05,0.0077470965,-0.016221706,-0.029639374,0.026158487,-0.0076687136,-0.0379971,-0.05411149,-0.014617873,-0.035137404,0.028240155,-0.0503537,-0.011822696,-0.06835617,0.060908817,0.044546496,-0.0021924917,0.08266615,-0.0069339667,0.033387065,-0.007229854,-0.084053524,-0.043424804,-0.017190715,0.05631953,-0.018200513,0.035003826,-0.02494163,-0.0614904,-0.063862465,0.05176614,-0.032886613,0.0661211,0.041171398,-0.010808587,-0.07878083,-0.043549735,0.023643937,0.04914669,0.009107135,0.0023591246,-0.009825618,0.012267636,-0.03194607,0.052380044,0.077219516,0.05975664,-0.0035441392,0.07569791,-0.008598598,0.025429575,-0.035397083,-0.036040105,-0.044200722,-0.04255309,-0.020692581,0.058135893,-0.03882452,0.013776761,-0.073452406,-0.039370295,-0.094225