#### Tiến sĩ Trương Văn Nam
- **Kinh nghiệm:** Giảng viên tiếng Trung tại ĐH Công nghiệp Hà Nội, ĐH Phenikaa, ĐH Kinh doanh và Công nghệ Hà Nội; Thành viên Hiệp hội giảng dạy tiếng Trung Việt Nam; Bí thư Liên chi Đoàn Khoa tiếng Trung; Sáng lập CLB tiếng Trung; Hội trưởng Hội lưu học sinh Việt Nam tại Đại Liên; giáo viên tình nguyện Công trình Hy vọng (Trung Quốc); hướng dẫn viên du lịch; phiên dịch cho nhiều dự án (Samsung, thủy điện Chim Vàn, nhà máy xi măng X18…)', '[-0.1176492,0.052401032,0.006583725,-0.03680042,-0.017599292,0.018187938,0.042245895,-0.06834406,0.01418494,0.06941776,0.067130476,-0.0077494043,0.01868403,0.017306032,0.011304381,-0.052650813,-0.056085795,0.048201602,-0.09321905,0.06794509,0.09581433,-0.065176114,0.018152723,-0.061199643,-0.023739275,-0.028996112,0.0503357,0.047479603,-0.0714145,-0.1359306,-0.047623564,0.043128595,-0.005077242,-0.007273662,0.0490017,-0.08712248,-0.02306408,0.05457285,0.03352618,0.037251405,-0.035243664,-0.037569,0.030174673,-0.06387768,0.044412587,0.0006481948,-0.056411844,-0.0628967,0.06050685,0.0023263264,-0.061731584,-0.012927997,0.058481812,0.042189896,-0.0061312937,0.059330795,0.019431071,0.04398961,0.09532612,0.07993205,0.044090074,0.050733805,-0.11679097,0.13415517,0.064555325,0.068975255,-0.016814534,-0.014929227,-0.017378038,-0.03315359,0.0064351647,0.028858703,0.019741891,0.056188773,-0.07055715,0.08156659,0.046508636,0.055767585,-0.093842186,-0.031458367,-0.051455677,-0.05350487,-0.019825667,0.021062547,-0.031499155,0.014619008,0.01917427,-0.014078614,-0.05784175,-0.0471085,-0.008459979,-0.038924403,0.0051172674,-0.06570314,-0.011944228,-0.07935217,0.04579011,0.030202204,-0.054365944,0.087819494,-0.0017746018,0.023997856,-0.040914357,-0.101659335,-0.04989906,-0.007880135,0.033397514,-0.0074543143,0.02746366,-0.034378313,-0.07693606,-0.017114228,0.024432907,-0.03491287,0.041143462,0.039478663,-0.011342169,-0.07538867,-0.034997728,0.01638349,0.011519318,0.0006327421,-0.015545686,-0.039566442,0.04804086,-0.020180129,0.07615616,0.0648525