### 3. Cán bộ coi thi (CBCT)
- Có mặt trước giờ 30 phút.
- Báo ngay nếu vắng mặt vì bất khả kháng (trước 45 phút) để thay thế.
- Không sử dụng điện thoại, không ra ngoài, không hút thuốc trong phòng thi.
- Ghi đầy đủ tiêu thức trên danh sách và túi bài, xếp bài theo danh sách, 2 CBCT cùng ký niêm phong.', '[-0.101801954,0.03647107,0.009143568,0.0019837404,-0.033952814,0.05041791,0.02658679,-0.069003224,0.017186804,0.078325644,0.08798579,-0.04066715,-0.05893992,0.030156711,0.008769569,-0.045755196,-0.054273985,0.0696921,-0.07368836,0.007150614,0.07756999,-0.048135348,0.004888738,-0.057689812,-0.026783904,-0.021099064,0.034506675,0.066079766,-0.04930185,-0.13729897,-0.03669859,0.016520899,0.0025184818,-0.033918962,0.058112282,-0.05129436,-0.02171129,0.075054884,0.035707153,0.05976212,-0.05010127,-0.026482977,0.01539062,-0.022302378,-0.0005757075,0.0035742237,-0.077356495,-0.07603252,0.070686825,0.033998366,-0.08830976,-0.0050082193,0.05800972,0.04431431,0.010796126,0.02627514,-0.0025795146,0.021661598,0.092585385,0.1051935,0.02591401,0.06828367,-0.12027268,0.15670109,0.08776291,0.06756153,-0.017418962,0.013338753,-0.0028409294,-0.018783126,0.0033933127,0.03703962,-0.012991377,0.036077064,-0.04518281,0.06342396,0.035788704,0.07978189,-0.1033701,-0.05078145,-0.015336586,0.0049839136,-0.0027421187,0.012201151,-0.026369395,-0.042883106,0.031630773,0.0042392486,-0.03140012,-0.022946876,0.0070550973,-0.032628566,0.01665206,-0.04042807,-0.046593156,-0.05702201,0.06363491,0.044735458,-0.024449782,0.09244946,-0.008968617,0.037075207,-0.026116917,-0.0685169,-0.05921455,-0.01652503,0.042934153,-0.029976213,0.059031114,-0.0063257255,-0.039520025,-0.04631959,0.0339874,-0.038080867,0.05302406,0.04219662,-0.06522956,-0.095307425,-0.03707965,0.027156314,0.03533624,-0.0032338658,-0.018854024,-0.033405464,0.042588454,-0.041767925,0.031068409,0.074204944,0.0485199,0.009729611,0.058503658,-0.0017980076,0.014023455,-0.037257638,-0.04573974,-0.046632323,-0.030696094,-0.044231158,0.05526862,-0.04338433,0.011418994,-0.10102376,-0.022495307,-0.109254315,0.027779032,0.094656594,-0.064885646,0.020310795,-0.060606077,-0.0741542,-0.0014231117,-0.022714382,0.07503452,-0.012591765,0.02131563,0.0079