### Các hoạt động nổi bật
> Tổ chức hội thảo, seminar, sự kiện văn hóa – nghệ thuật – thể thao (bơi lội, bóng đá, chèo thuyền…). Hoạt động tình nguyện: “Chiến binh hoa quả”, “Tết yêu thương”, “Tết đong đầy”, “Máu hồng”, “Tiếp sức mùa thi”, “Góp năng xuân”. Gây quỹ qua bán hoa quả, đồ dùng học tập.', '[-0.08113627,0.07071418,0.0010516477,-0.030228965,-0.027786603,0.06032363,0.045517787,-0.051892962,-0.008241266,0.06975064,0.030601637,-0.033832993,-0.04942878,0.02646993,0.032548796,-0.035351273,-0.030917205,0.091936655,-0.09032325,0.022257095,0.07550788,-0.044863135,0.0045932857,-0.0136527065,-0.03195776,-0.047721956,0.015008134,0.03832333,-0.009701592,-0.116466396,-0.030047841,0.034018725,0.022581212,-0.040069707,0.040496714,-0.06747132,-0.024236664,0.05945676,0.029814396,0.024802858,-0.048573703,-0.044711486,0.025472505,-0.06728204,0.009700088,-0.0018222139,-0.071134515,-0.065701805,0.06673715,0.032604598,-0.0936598,-0.0091509195,0.042295765,0.006713775,0.009724726,0.07292518,0.037160747,0.030513484,0.07185659,0.09501128,0.027002338,0.06298496,-0.14961547,0.18373649,0.06434375,0.047473818,-0.037591044,0.046770234,-0.0027047368,-0.022098536,0.031887803,0.029263586,0.020725017,0.055046488,-0.058383252,0.058985744,0.04699283,0.0878999,-0.09004578,-0.005149346,-0.007846417,-0.029143555,-0.04520114,0.013420315,-0.03493337,-0.0283507,0.020389536,-0.040426027,-0.038541295,-0.043962963,-0.003418354,-0.05107355,-0.005853964,-0.04203986,-0.011784316,-0.05669592,0.06529955,0.046811465,-0.04062247,0.09104467,0.012840734,0.021697879,-0.01719817,-0.08054985,-0.0330964,-0.04277968,0.018519523,-0.03702909,0.05127011,0.05274037,-0.063654676,-0.05652996,0.02637755,-0.060204387,0.029695168,0.04470448,-0.008146124,-0.06908771,-0.027174452,0.033971008,0.033465132,-0.011687745,-0.015747875,-0.020138873,0.05461015,-0.029795568,0.032850143,0.033226807,0.07696348,-0.056953713,0.059781555,-0.032529376,-0.0023284177,-0.03879634,-0.043995198,-0.05966268,-0.0078958785,-0.03318403,0.062028304,-0.042470325,0.006024815,-0.